### Get Access Token 
# @name requestAccessToken
POST {{$dotenv ariba_scim_token_endpoint}}?grant_type=openapi_2lo&id={{$dotenv ariba_scim_realm}}
Authorization: Basic {{$dotenv ariba_scim_clientid}}:{{$dotenv ariba_scim_clientsecret}}
Cache-Control: no-cache
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

#&response_type=token

### Fill Variables from Response
@access_token = {{requestAccessToken.response.body.$.access_token}}
### Read Users
GET {{$dotenv ias_scim_endpoint}}/scim/Users
Authorization: Basic {{$dotenv ias_scim_username}}:{{$dotenv ias_scim_password}}
